PrecisEnactment of an ORDER RESPECTING THE WITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL OF CERTAIN LANDS IN THE YUKON TERRITORY (LHUTSAW WETLAND HABITAT PROTECTION AREA, Y.T.) - which (a) provides for the withdrawal from disposal of certain tracts of land in the Yukon until August 31, 2005, and (b) repeals the Withdrawal from Disposal Order made by Order in Council P.C. 1997-1190.
